  "description": "Only transcripts we can accept Upload exactly one of the four types below ✓ Accepted formats Why we’re picky Our transcript automation relies on consistent, mac",
  "content": "<div class=\"paper-wrap tm-anim\">\n        <article class=\"paper\">\n          <div class=\"paper-inner\">\n\n            <header class=\"paper-header\">\n              <div>\n                <h1>Only transcripts we can accept</h1>\n                <p>Upload exactly one of the four types below</p>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"badge accepted\">✓ Accepted formats</div>\n            </header>\n\n            <section class=\"section\">\n              <div class=\"section-title\">Why we’re picky</div>\n              <div class=\"callout\">\n                Our transcript automation relies on consistent, machine-readable sections.\n                If the transcript doesn’t match these four formats, it either fails parsing or produces bad results.\n                Bad results are fun for nobody.\n              </div>\n            </section>\n\n            <section class=\"section\">\n              <div class=\"section-title\">Accepted Transcript Types</div>\n\n              <div class=\"callout\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px;\">\n                Use this page as a visual checklist. Each accepted type has its own section below with a sample that matches the IRS layout.\n                Your upload should look like these, including the first-page header.\n              </div>\n\n              <nav aria-label=\"Transcript type navigation\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px;\">\n                <div class=\"grid\" style=\"grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); gap: 10px;\">\n                  <a href=\"#account-transcript\" class=\"badge accepted\" style=\"justify-content: center; text-decoration: none;\">Account Transcript</a>\n                  <a href=\"#record-of-account\" class=\"badge accepted\" style=\"justify-content: center; text-decoration: none;\">Record of Account Transcript</a>\n                  <a href=\"#tax-return-transcript\" class=\"badge accepted\" style=\"justify-content: center; text-decoration: none;\">Tax Return Transcript</a>\n                  <a href=\"#wage-income\" class=\"badge accepted\" style=\"justify-content: center; text-decoration: none;\">Wage and Income Transcript</a>\n                </div>\n              </nav>\n\n              <!-- 1) Account Transcript -->\n              <section id=\"account-transcript\" class=\"section\" style=\"margin-bottom: 34px;\">\n                <div class=\"section-title\">Account Transcript</div>\n                <div class=\"callout\" style=\"margin-bottom: 14px;\">\n                  Used for balances, accruals, and transaction code activity. This transcript usually includes an “Information from the return or as adjusted” block and balance lines.\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"card\">\n                  <div class=\"card-top\">\n                    <div>\n                      <h2 class=\"card-title\">What it should look like</h2>\n                      <p class=\"card-sub\">First page includes the exact sensitive-data header + the “Form 1040 Account Transcript” title.</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"badge accepted\">Accepted</div>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"preview\">\n                    <div class=\"preview-box\" role=\"region\" aria-label=\"Account Transcript sample\" style=\"overflow-x: auto;\">\n                      <div class=\"irs-sample\">\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-line irs-center\">Internal Revenue Service</div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-line irs-center preview-muted\">United States Department of the Treasury</div>\n                        <div class=\"mini-rule\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-line irs-center\" style=\"border: 2px solid #0b0a14; padding: 2px 8px;\">This Product Contains Sensitive Taxpayer Data</div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-gap\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-title irs-center\">Form 1040 Account Transcript</div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-grid irs-topmeta\">\n                          <div class=\"irs-left\"></div>\n                          <div class=\"irs-right\">\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Request Date:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">MM-DD-YYYY</span></div>\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Response Date:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">MM-DD-YYYY</span></div>\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Tracking Number:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">###########</span></div>\n                          </div>\n                        </div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-gap\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Form Number:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">1040</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Report for Tax Period Ending:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">MM-DD-YYYY</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Taxpayer Identification Number:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">XXX-XX-XXXX</span></div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-gap\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-block\">TAXPAYER NAME</div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-block\">ADDRESS LINE</div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-block\">CITY, ST ZIP</div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-gap\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-center\">--- Any minus sign shown below signifies a credit amount ---</div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-gap\"></div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-grid\">\n                          <div class=\"irs-left\">\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Account balance:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$0.00</span></div>\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Accrued interest:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$0.00</span></div>\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Accrued penalty:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$0.00</span></div>\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Account balance plus accruals (this is not a payoff amount):</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$0.00</span></div>\n                          </div>\n                          <div class=\"irs-right\">\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">As of:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">MM-DD-YYYY</span></div>\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">As of:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">MM-DD-YYYY</span></div>\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">As of:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">MM-DD-YYYY</span></div>\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">As of:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">MM-DD-YYYY</span></div>\n                          </div>\n                        </div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-gap\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-center\">** Information from the return or as adjusted **</div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-gap\"></div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-grid\">\n                          <div class=\"irs-left\">\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Exemptions:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">01</span></div>\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Filing status:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">Single</span></div>\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Adjusted gross income:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$0.00</span></div>\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Taxable income:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$0.00</span></div>\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Tax per return:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$0.00</span></div>\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">SE taxable income taxpayer:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$0.00</span></div>\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">SE taxable income spouse:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$0.00</span></div>\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Total self employment tax:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$0.00</span></div>\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Return due date or return received date (whichever is later):</span><span class=\"irs-v\">MM-DD-YYYY</span></div>\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Processing date:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">MM-DD-YYYY</span></div>\n                          </div>\n                          <div class=\"irs-right\"></div>\n                        </div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-gap\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-center irs-strong\">TRANSACTIONS</div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-gap\"></div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-line irs-strong\">CODE  EXPLANATION OF TRANSACTION                         CYCLE     DATE        AMOUNT</div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-line\">150   Tax return filed                                   ######    MM-DD-YYYY   $0.00</div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-line\">      29221-137-64010-5</div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-gap\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-line irs-center\">This Product Contains Sensitive Taxpayer Data</div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-line irs-center\">Page 1/1</div>$1</div>\n                </div>\n              </section>\n\n              <!-- 2) Record of Account Transcript -->\n              <section id=\"record-of-account\" class=\"section\" style=\"margin-bottom: 34px;\">\n                <div class=\"section-title\">Record of Account Transcript</div>\n                <div class=\"callout\" style=\"margin-bottom: 14px;\">\n                  Combines return details and account activity in one document. It often looks like an Account Transcript plus return-summary fields.\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"card\">\n                  <div class=\"card-top\">\n                    <div>\n                      <h2 class=\"card-title\">What it should look like</h2>\n                      <p class=\"card-sub\">IRS header + boxed sensitive-data line + “Form 1040 Record of Account” title, with right-aligned request/response/tracking.</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"badge accepted\">Accepted</div>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"preview\">\n                    <div class=\"preview-box\" role=\"region\" aria-label=\"Record of Account Transcript sample\" style=\"overflow-x: auto;\">\n                      <div class=\"irs-sample\">\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-line irs-center\">Internal Revenue Service</div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-line irs-center preview-muted\">United States Department of the Treasury</div>\n                        <div class=\"mini-rule\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-line irs-center\" style=\"border: 2px solid #0b0a14; padding: 2px 8px;\">This Product Contains Sensitive Taxpayer Data</div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-gap\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-title irs-center\">Form 1040 Record of Account</div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-grid irs-topmeta\">\n                          <div class=\"irs-left\"></div>\n                          <div class=\"irs-right\">\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Request Date:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">MM-DD-YYYY</span></div>\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Response Date:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">MM-DD-YYYY</span></div>\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Tracking Number:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">###########</span></div>\n                          </div>\n                        </div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-gap\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Form Number:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">1040</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Report for Tax Period Ending:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">MM-DD-YYYY</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Taxpayer Identification Number:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">XXX-XX-XXXX</span></div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-gap\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-block\">TAXPAYER NAME</div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-block\">ADDRESS LINE</div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-block\">CITY, ST ZIP</div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-gap\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-center\">--- Any minus sign shown below signifies a credit amount ---</div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-gap\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-grid\">\n                          <div class=\"irs-left\">\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Account balance:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$0.00</span></div>\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Accrued interest:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$0.00</span></div>\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Accrued penalty:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$0.00</span></div>\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Account balance plus accruals (this is not a payoff amount):</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$0.00</span></div>\n                          </div>\n                          <div class=\"irs-right\">\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">As of:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">MM-DD-YYYY</span></div>\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">As of:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">MM-DD-YYYY</span></div>\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">As of:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">MM-DD-YYYY</span></div>\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">As of:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">MM-DD-YYYY</span></div>\n                          </div>\n                        </div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-gap\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-center\">** Information from the return or as adjusted **</div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-gap\"></div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-grid\">\n                          <div class=\"irs-left\">\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Exemptions:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">01</span></div>\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Filing status:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">Single</span></div>\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Adjusted gross income:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$0.00</span></div>\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Taxable income:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$0.00</span></div>\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Tax per return:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$0.00</span></div>\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Processing date:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">MM-DD-YYYY</span></div>\n                          </div>\n                          <div class=\"irs-right\"></div>\n                        </div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-gap\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-center irs-strong\">TRANSACTIONS</div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-gap\"></div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-line irs-strong\">CODE  EXPLANATION OF TRANSACTION                         CYCLE     DATE        AMOUNT</div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-line\">150   Tax return filed                                   ######    MM-DD-YYYY   $0.00</div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-line\">      29221-137-64010-5</div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-gap\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">SSN provided:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">XXX-XX-XXXX</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Report for Tax Period Ending:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">MM-DD-YYYY</span></div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-gap\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-paragraph irs-strong\">The following items reflect the amount as shown on the return, and the amount as adjusted, if applicable. They do not show subsequent activity on the account.</div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-gap\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-line irs-center\">This Product Contains Sensitive Taxpayer Data</div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-line irs-center\">Page 1/6</div>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </section>\n\n              <!-- 3) Tax Return Transcript -->\n              <section id=\"tax-return-transcript\" class=\"section\" style=\"margin-bottom: 34px;\">\n                <div class=\"section-title\">Tax Return Transcript</div>\n                <div class=\"callout\" style=\"margin-bottom: 14px;\">\n                  Shows line items from the filed return (income, adjustments, credits). It typically states that it does not show subsequent activity on the account.\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"card\">\n                  <div class=\"card-top\">\n                    <div>\n                      <h2 class=\"card-title\">What it should look like</h2>\n                      <p class=\"card-sub\">First page includes the sensitive-data header + the “Form 1040 Tax Return Transcript” title, with right-aligned request/response/tracking.</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"badge accepted\">Accepted</div>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"preview\">\n                    <div class=\"preview-box\" role=\"region\" aria-label=\"Tax Return Transcript sample\" style=\"overflow-x: auto;\">\n                      <div class=\"irs-sample\">\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-line irs-center\">Internal Revenue Service</div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-line irs-center preview-muted\">United States Department of the Treasury</div>\n                        <div class=\"mini-rule\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-line irs-center\">This Product Contains Sensitive Taxpayer Data</div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-gap\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-title irs-center\">Form 1040 Tax Return Transcript</div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-grid irs-topmeta\">\n                          <div class=\"irs-left\"></div>\n                          <div class=\"irs-right\">\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Request Date:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">MM-DD-YYYY</span></div>\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Response Date:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">MM-DD-YYYY</span></div>\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Tracking Number:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">###########</span></div>\n                          </div>\n                        </div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-gap\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">SSN provided:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">XXX-XX-XXXX</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Report for Tax Period Ending:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">MM-DD-YYYY</span></div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-gap\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-paragraph irs-strong\">The following items reflect the amount as shown on the return, and the amount as adjusted, if applicable. They do not show subsequent activity on the account.</div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-gap\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">SSN:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">XXX-XX-XXXX</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Spouse SSN:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">&nbsp;</span></div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-gap\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-block\">TAXPAYER NAME</div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-block\">ADDRESS LINE</div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-block\">CITY, ST ZIP</div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-gap\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Filing status:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">Single Taxpayer</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Form number:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">1040</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Cycle posted:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">######</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Received date:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">MM-DD-YYYY</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Payment:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$0.00</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Exemption number:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">01</span></div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-gap\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-center irs-strong\">Income</div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-gap\"></div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span>Total wages:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$0.00</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span>Form W-2 wages:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$0.00</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span>Taxable interest income (Schedule B):</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$0.00</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span>Tax-exempt interest:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$0.00</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span>Ordinary dividend income (Schedule B):</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$0.00</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span>Qualified dividends:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$0.00</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span>Refunds of state/local taxes:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$0.00</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span>Alimony received:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$0.00</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span>Business income or loss (Schedule C):</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$0.00</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span>Capital gain or loss (Schedule D):</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$0.00</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span>Other gain or loss (Form 4797):</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$0.00</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span>Total IRA distributions:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$0.00</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span>Taxable IRA distributions:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$0.00</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span>Total pensions and annuities:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$0.00</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span>Taxable pension/annuity amount:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$0.00</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span>Additional income:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$0.00</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span>Adjusted gross income per computer:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$0.00</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span>Refundable credits per computer:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$0.00</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span>Nonrefundable education credit per computer:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$0.00</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span>Qualified business income deduction:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$0.00</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span>Rent/royalty/partnership/estate (Schedule E) per computer:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$0.00</span></div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-gap\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-line irs-center\">This Product Contains Sensitive Taxpayer Data</div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-line irs-center\">Page 1/1</div>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </section>\n\n              <!-- 4) Wage and Income Transcript -->\n              <section id=\"wage-income\" class=\"section\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">\n                <div class=\"section-title\">Wage and Income Transcript</div>\n                <div class=\"callout\" style=\"margin-bottom: 14px;\">\n                  Lists third-party information returns (W-2, 1099 series, brokerage, etc.). The first section commonly starts with “Form W-2 Wage and Tax Statement.”\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"card\">\n                  <div class=\"card-top\">\n                    <div>\n                      <h2 class=\"card-title\">What it should look like</h2>\n                      <p class=\"card-sub\">IRS header + boxed sensitive-data line + “Wage and Income Transcript” title, with right-aligned request/response/tracking.</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"badge accepted\">Accepted</div>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"preview\">\n                    <div class=\"preview-box\" role=\"region\" aria-label=\"Wage and Income Transcript sample\" style=\"overflow-x: auto;\">\n                      <div class=\"irs-sample\">\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-line irs-center\">Internal Revenue Service</div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-line irs-center preview-muted\">United States Department of the Treasury</div>\n                        <div class=\"mini-rule\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-line irs-center\" style=\"border: 2px solid #0b0a14; padding: 2px 8px;\">This Product Contains Sensitive Taxpayer Data</div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-gap\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-title irs-center\">Wage and Income Transcript</div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-grid irs-topmeta\">\n                          <div class=\"irs-left\">\n                            <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">TIN Provided:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">XXX-XX-XXXX</span></div>\n                            <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Tax Period Requested:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">MM-DD-YYYY</span></div>\n                          </div>\n                          <div class=\"irs-right\">\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Request Date:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">MM-DD-YYYY</span></div>\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Response Date:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">MM-DD-YYYY</span></div>\n                            <div class=\"irs-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Tracking Number:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">###########</span></div>\n                          </div>\n                        </div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-gap\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-center irs-strong\">Form W-2 Wage and Tax Statement</div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-gap\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-block irs-strong\">Employer:</div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Employer Identification Number (EIN):</span><span class=\"irs-v\">XX-XXXXXXX</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-block\">EMPLOYER NAME</div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-block\">ADDRESS LINE</div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-block\">CITY, ST ZIP</div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-gap\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-block irs-strong\">Employee:</div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Employee's Social Security Number:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">XXX-XX-XXXX</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-block\">TAXPAYER NAME</div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-block\">ADDRESS LINE</div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-gap\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Submission Type:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">Original document</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Wages, Tips and Other Compensation:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$X,XXX.00</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Federal Income Tax Withheld:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$XXX.00</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Social Security Wages:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$X,XXX.00</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Social Security Tax Withheld:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$XXX.00</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Medicare Wages and Tips:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$X,XXX.00</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Medicare Tax Withheld:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">$XXX.00</span></div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-gap\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-center irs-strong\">Form 1099-B Proceeds from Broker and Barter Exchange Transactions</div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-gap\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-block irs-strong\">Payer:</div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Payer's Federal Identification Number (FIN):</span><span class=\"irs-v\">XX-XXXXXXX</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-block\">PAYER NAME</div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-block\">ADDRESS LINE</div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-gap\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-block irs-strong\">Recipient:</div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-wide-row\"><span class=\"irs-k\">Recipient's identification number:</span><span class=\"irs-v\">XXX-XX-XXXX</span></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-block\">TAXPAYER NAME</div>\n\n                        <div class=\"irs-gap\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-line irs-center\">This Product Contains Sensitive Taxpayer Data</div>\n                        <div class=\"irs-line irs-center\">Page 1/2</div>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </section>\n            </section>\n\n            <section class=\"section\">\n              <div class=\"section-title\">What we do not accept</div>\n              <ul class=\"list\">\n                <li>Photos of a screen (low contrast, skew, missing edges)</li>\n                <li>Partial pages (missing the first page header area)</li>\n                <li>Redacted or edited transcripts (we need the full structure to parse)</li>\n                <li>\"Tax Compliance Report\" style summaries (not an IRS transcript)</li>\n              </ul>\n            </section>\n\n            <section class=\"section\">\n              <div class=\"section-title\">Quick self-check</div>\n              <ul class=\"list\">\n                <li>First page includes the phrase “This Product Contains Sensitive Taxpayer Data”</li>\n                <li>\n                  Title clearly says one of the following:<br>\n                  Account Transcript, Record of Account, Tax Return Transcript, Wage and Income Transcript\n                </li>\n                <li>The PDF is selectable text (you can highlight text, not just an image)</li>\n                <li>You included every page from page 1 to the last page</li>\n              </ul>\n            </section>\n\n            <div class=\"footer-note\">\n              <span>Transcripts contain sensitive taxpayer data. Upload directly through this secure portal for automated processing.</span>\n              <span>Generated <span id=\"doc-date\"></span></span>\n            </div>\n\n          </div>\n        </article>\n      </div>",
